See Shinedown like you`ve never seen them before... raw & powerful. Recorded on the very last performance after 2 years of touring during their break-out year, see why Shinedown has become one of the greatest rock bands in the country.

Also get a sneak peak behind the band, with a bonus documentary and commentary from the band themselves, exclusive photos, videos, and other bonus features.
